0:00:00.000,0:00:02.580
Good morning, church!

0:00:02.580,0:00:03.980
[Good morning.]

0:00:03.980,0:00:06.980
ACTING ON THE WORD

0:00:06.980,0:00:08.060
Hallelujah.

0:00:08.060,0:00:10.580
[Amen.]

0:00:10.580,0:00:30.280
Acting on the Word demands for believing and believing demands action – creates action.

0:00:30.280,0:00:32.460
It is not just mental assent.

0:00:32.460,0:00:39.500
It does not just admire or admit without acting upon it.

0:00:39.500,0:00:43.540
Action!

0:00:43.540,0:00:47.620
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:00:47.620,0:00:54.260
Now, it is time to bring Jesus one the scene.

0:00:54.260,0:01:00.660
The direction to follow - you have seen it all.

0:01:00.660,0:01:05.840
How do we bring Jesus on the scene?

0:01:05.840,0:01:10.000
When you say, "In Jesus' name" and Jesus would just come.

0:01:10.000,0:01:12.980
Ask your neighbour, “How do we bring Jesus on the scene?”

0:01:12.980,0:01:14.840
[How do we bring Jesus on the scene?]

0:01:14.840,0:01:15.920
I cannot hear you.

0:01:15.920,0:01:18.160
[How do we bring Jesus on the scene?]

0:01:18.160,0:01:19.180
I cannot hear you.

0:01:19.180,0:01:20.980
[How do we bring Jesus on the scene?]

0:01:20.980,0:01:22.520
How do we bring Jesus on the scene?

0:01:22.520,0:01:28.340
There are many: "be healed, be delivered, amen" but Jesus is not there.

0:01:28.340,0:01:30.220
You are just saying words.

0:01:30.220,0:01:35.080
There is a difference between praying prayer and saying words.

0:01:35.080,0:01:36.440
There is a difference between what?

0:01:36.440,0:01:45.980
Praying prayer and saying words.

0:01:45.980,0:01:54.920
Acting on the Word is letting Christ act through you.

0:01:54.920,0:01:56.000
Tell your neighbour.

0:01:56.000,0:02:03.560
[Acting on the Word is letting Christ act through you.]

0:02:03.560,0:02:20.960
I mean, acting on the Word then gives Christ an opportunity to heal, deliver and set you free.

0:02:20.960,0:02:23.160
Action!

0:02:23.160,0:02:36.260
He is looking for an opportunity to eat with you, talk to you, greet you; "How are you?", to touch you,

0:02:36.260,0:02:40.500
to live with you - just an opportunity.

0:02:40.500,0:02:52.980
By acting on the Word then gives Christ an opportunity.

0:02:52.980,0:03:10.440
By looking into the Word and acting on it will bring Christ on the scene.

0:03:10.440,0:03:23.780
The problem of believing is made easy when you know that it is acting on what God has spoken.

0:03:23.780,0:03:24.780
Repeat after me.

0:03:24.780,0:03:38.800
The problem of believing is made easy when you know that it is acting on what God has spoken -

0:03:38.800,0:03:42.340
very very...

0:03:42.340,0:03:44.380
it is made simple.

0:03:44.380,0:03:50.660
Faith is perfected by our acting on the Word.

0:03:50.660,0:04:03.740
The problem of believing is made very simple when you know that it is acting on what Jesus has spoken.

0:04:03.740,0:04:09.100
Love your neighbour as yourself, thou shalt not kill, thou shalt not steal -

0:04:09.100,0:04:14.060
just act on those things - the commandments.

0:04:14.060,0:04:23.020
It is so simple, when you know that it is acting on what He has spoken.

0:04:23.020,0:04:28.100
You will be talking about me but you cannot behave like me.

0:04:28.100,0:04:36.860
If you are saying, "T.B. Joshua is this and that" - this is all you know about me.

0:04:36.860,0:04:40.020
But what of my behavior?

0:04:40.020,0:04:43.240
I can run - can you run?

0:04:43.240,0:04:48.300
I can laugh - will you also laugh?

0:04:48.300,0:04:51.280
I can dance - can you dance?

0:04:51.280,0:04:54.040
T.B. Joshua can run - can you run?

0:04:54.040,0:04:58.040
If you cannot run - you do not know T.B. Joshua.

0:04:58.040,0:05:02.000
This is the problem we are having in our faith today.

0:05:02.000,0:05:06.760
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:05:06.760,0:05:08.160
Say, "Action!"

0:05:08.160,0:05:09.180
[Action!]

0:05:09.180,0:05:15.880
Believing demands action – creates action.

0:05:15.880,0:05:19.080
That is believing.

0:05:19.080,0:05:24.460
We are hearers but not doers.

0:05:24.460,0:05:34.140
Since you are a hearer, you just have sense knowledge – mental assent.

0:05:34.140,0:05:41.420
Being just a hearer and not a doer – if there is anything you have faith in, it is in man;

0:05:41.420,0:05:46.400
what man has done – science, works and organization.

0:05:46.400,0:05:48.680
These are the things you can have faith in - not in God.

0:05:48.680,0:05:55.220
To have faith in God, you must be a doer of the Word.

0:05:55.220,0:05:57.840
If you are a doer, you have faith in God

0:05:57.840,0:06:03.240
but if you are just a hearer of the Word, if there is anything you have faith in,

0:06:03.240,0:06:14.100
is in man – what man has done, science, works and organization and more.

0:06:14.100,0:06:23.040
These are the things you can have faith in because you are not a doer of the Word.

0:06:23.040,0:06:36.240
That is why you can build a big beautiful church, you can organize things, you are a good organizer,

0:06:36.240,0:06:43.180
you can plan an organization or church, you can build a big building...

0:06:43.180,0:06:49.240
Science - yes, you can make things happen just like that.

0:06:49.240,0:06:51.840
These are man's natural gifts.

0:06:51.840,0:06:58.100
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:06:58.100,0:07:12.780
This does not necessarily demand for an obedience to God to be endowed naturally.

0:07:12.780,0:07:20.740
You learn, you study, you pay the price.

0:07:20.740,0:07:25.080
Can you see now why it is difficult for you to have faith in God?

0:07:25.080,0:07:36.260
You hear and study the Word of God, you commit it to memory, not in your heart.

0:07:36.260,0:07:46.980
If there is anything you have faith in - it is in what man has done.

0:07:46.980,0:07:53.800
These are the things you have faith in because you are a hearer and not a doer.

0:07:53.800,0:07:58.940
That is "a sense knowledge, mental assent" which I describe as

0:07:58.940,0:08:09.420
"admires, admits but does not act on the Word".

0:08:09.420,0:08:14.640
I admire your look, you look good.

0:08:14.640,0:08:18.560
That does not mean I can die for you.

0:08:18.560,0:08:20.480
There is an extent I can go...

0:08:20.480,0:08:25.420
These are the reasons you look at the appearance when you want to marry.

0:08:25.420,0:08:35.060
The man is rich, looks handsome, the lady looks beautiful - they have some outward qualities.

0:08:35.060,0:08:38.320
This is mental assent.

0:08:38.320,0:08:48.440
If you go now “by believing” to marry somebody and carry God along, you demand for action,

0:08:48.440,0:08:55.500
create an action - and this must come from your heart.

0:08:55.500,0:09:00.500
The Bible says that what does not come from the heart is a sin.

0:09:00.500,0:09:03.600
Action must come from your heart.

0:09:03.600,0:09:07.380
Heart.

0:09:07.380,0:09:15.600
The love of the heart is love of God.

0:09:15.600,0:09:18.260
Tell your neighbour, “I have found the secret”.

0:09:18.260,0:09:19.860
[I have found the secret.]

0:09:19.860,0:09:20.720
I cannot hear you.

0:09:20.720,0:09:22.440
[I have found the secret.]

0:09:22.440,0:09:23.460
I cannot hear you.

0:09:23.460,0:09:25.160
[I have found the secret.]

0:09:25.160,0:09:32.600
Let the Word be loosed in you, let the Word dominate you,

0:09:32.600,0:09:38.300
let the Word rule you, let the Word live in you.

0:09:38.400,0:09:41.340
These are the secrets.

0:09:41.340,0:09:45.860
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:09:45.860,0:09:49.060
I have found the secret.

0:09:49.060,0:09:58.880
Let the Word rule you, let the Word be loosed in you, let the Word dominate you, let the Word live in you -

0:09:58.880,0:10:07.280
These are the secrets of bringing Jesus on the scene.

0:10:07.280,0:10:09.400
The secret of bringing what?

0:10:09.400,0:10:12.820
[These are the secrets of bringing Jesus on the scene.]

0:10:12.820,0:10:19.600
Each time you call, "Jesus!" - people around would hear you, you would hear yourself but Jesus does not what?

0:10:19.600,0:10:20.460
[Hear you.]

0:10:20.460,0:10:23.240
Does not hear you - that is very frustrating.

0:10:23.240,0:10:30.160
This is what happened to the seven sons of Sceva; when Jesus could not hear them - what happened?

0:10:30.160,0:10:37.480
The demon jumped on them and said, "Paul I know, Jesus I know; but who are you?"

0:10:37.480,0:10:39.720
They started beating them.

0:10:39.720,0:10:45.600
If Jesus heard them Jesus would be there to act for them, to defend them, to protect them.

0:10:45.600,0:10:47.440
OK, take your pen and write,

0:10:47.440,0:10:53.540
“The secret of bringing Jesus on the scene, I have found it today.”

0:10:53.540,0:10:55.480
I cannot hear you.

0:10:55.480,0:11:02.660
I have found the secret, the secret of bringing Jesus on the scene:

0:11:02.660,0:11:16.720
Let the Word be loosed in you, let the Word dominate you, let the Word rule you, let the Word live in you.

0:11:16.720,0:11:18.660
That is the secret.

0:11:18.660,0:11:21.280
That is just the secret.

0:11:21.280,0:11:26.680
Loose is  l o o s e.

0:11:26.680,0:11:30.820
Once you have this; you will be eating with Jesus...

0:11:30.820,0:11:34.740
When you say "Jesus!", 
He will reply, "What do you want?"

0:11:34.740,0:11:38.300
You would say, "Be healed!"

0:11:38.300,0:11:41.900
You say, "Jesus!", He would reply, 
"- What do you want?

0:11:41.900,0:11:48.000
- I want you to come sleep with me.
- OK, don't worry. Give me another pillow."

0:11:48.000,0:11:49.960
[Hallelujah]

0:11:49.960,0:11:53.360
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:11:53.360,0:12:03.140
You can see the reason why you are just calling yourself every day instead of Jesus.

0:12:03.140,0:12:05.700
If you don’t give, you don’t receive.

0:12:05.700,0:12:23.960
In this case now, you have to give to receive; not money – your quality time, strength and love.

0:12:23.960,0:12:33.880
You must give your quality time to the Word of God, your quality love to the Word of God.

0:12:33.880,0:12:37.380
If you were not here but at home - where can you go?

0:12:37.380,0:12:39.640
Can you go to work today?

0:12:39.640,0:12:41.400
Can you go to the bank?

0:12:41.400,0:12:47.700
Today is not your quality time.

0:12:47.700,0:12:50.760
You know what I'm talking about.

0:12:50.760,0:12:53.540
Today is not your quality time.

0:12:53.540,0:12:58.700
Your quality time is when you are in between a billion dollars...

0:12:58.700,0:13:04.920
Here is prayer and somebody is calling you, 
"- Hey, come and receive this.

0:13:04.920,0:13:12.760
- No, I want to pray. When I finish the prayer I will come.
- If you come after prayer you will miss the money.

0:13:12.760,0:13:15.440
- OK, let me miss the money. Let me pray first."

0:13:15.440,0:13:18.340
How many of us can do that?

0:13:18.340,0:13:22.280
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:13:22.280,0:13:29.300
Choice can be the greatest gift you have.

0:13:29.300,0:13:35.300
There are many of us today that were supposed to be here and I can see that one or two them are not around.

0:13:35.300,0:13:43.600
By the time you meet them, they will say that while they were coming to the church they received a phone call

0:13:43.600,0:13:50.940
that their dear one was in coma.

0:13:50.940,0:13:54.200
It is a time for a choice now.

0:13:54.200,0:14:00.840
Would you choose to go to your dear one that is in coma or come to God?

0:14:00.840,0:14:05.780
Who is the Creator of the one that is in coma?

0:14:05.780,0:14:13.460
God is not one of those things, He is the Only one.

0:14:13.460,0:14:16.760
Even your coming here can revive the one in coma.

0:14:16.760,0:14:18.060
[Amen.]

0:14:18.060,0:14:25.020
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:14:25.020,0:14:33.280
You don't put God where God belongs - that is the problem you are having now.

0:14:33.280,0:14:37.500
In the house of many of us - we don't have an altar.

0:14:37.500,0:14:48.480
You are leaving the church now, you get back home; the morning water you received - you take it there.

0:14:48.480,0:14:53.700
Your Bible, your booklet you received you place it there.

0:14:53.700,0:14:58.420
Before you enter your room or any other place, you go straight to the altar -

0:14:58.420,0:15:02.200
you go on your knees at the table of your altar -

0:15:02.200,0:15:10.500
you place everything you have received today (morning water...) on the table with your Bible

0:15:10.500,0:15:14.720
and give thanks to God for giving you the grace to come back home.

0:15:14.720,0:15:19.660
It is like you believe that Angels of God have followed from here; you take them back to your altar

0:15:19.660,0:15:23.160
to stay there for you - when you are going home...

0:15:23.160,0:15:28.880
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:15:28.880,0:15:40.380
When you just get home to your sitting room, bedroom you hang your clothes - "where is my food?"

0:15:40.380,0:15:42.340
You don't have an altar.

0:15:42.340,0:15:52.340
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:15:52.340,0:15:59.060
Sometimes, you just have a revelation that you want to fast and pray today

0:15:59.060,0:16:02.960
and you will only be at the altar there that day.

0:16:02.960,0:16:09.740
You tell your family, "I'm there" - you just lay down there and pray.

0:16:09.740,0:16:15.900
An altar should be a place where you should give the highest regard to God.

0:16:15.900,0:16:22.520
We see God as one of those things... No - He is the only, not one of those things.

0:16:22.520,0:16:28.080
Don't restrict God with arrangements you make.

0:16:28.080,0:16:32.660
That is why it is difficult for me to wear an expensive watch.

0:16:32.660,0:16:37.640
Because I cannot "time" God.

0:16:37.640,0:16:41.520
If I have a watch I will not look at it when I am in the presence of God.

0:16:41.520,0:16:42.720
I will not "time" Him.

0:16:42.720,0:16:47.260
He should tell me when to start and when to finish, or when I should leave here.

0:16:47.260,0:16:52.940
I should not to begin to look at the watch, "oh, this is twelve o'clock..."

0:16:52.940,0:16:54.740
I don't "time" Him.

0:16:54.740,0:16:59.560
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:16:59.560,0:17:08.200
These are the steps we are ignorantly taking and we say that we are serving God.

0:17:08.200,0:17:13.740
You are not serving God - it is God who is serving you.

0:17:13.740,0:17:18.960
Now, I’m looking at you; I can’t see anyone among you holding this.

0:17:18.960,0:17:27.320
While I'm talking I continue to "fire on" - and that is the purpose of it.

0:17:27.320,0:17:31.600
While I'm talking, you should also be in an attitude of prayer by saying,

0:17:31.600,0:17:35.900
"take more of me Lord, give me more of You."

0:17:35.900,0:17:44.700
If you cannot do that here, you will definitely forget about it at home while watching TV.

0:17:44.700,0:17:51.920
You should be "counting your faith" while watching TV.

0:17:51.920,0:17:53.520
You must get used to it.

0:17:53.520,0:17:59.620
You must cultivate the habit of building yourself – you need to build yourself.

0:17:59.620,0:18:02.760
When you build yourself, God will take it up -

0:18:02.760,0:18:06.060
God will take you somewhere and start building you

0:18:06.060,0:18:11.360
but you must first of all start building yourself before God can take it up and begin to build you.

0:18:11.360,0:18:14.620
God will not start building you from scratch.

0:18:14.620,0:18:18.660
Look at what happened to Peter  - I keep giving a good example of Peter.

0:18:18.660,0:18:24.500
When Peter wanted to meet Him on the sea, He said, "Come".

0:18:24.500,0:18:26.760
He said, "I want to come with You".

0:18:26.760,0:18:30.980
Jesus said, "Come. Take a step."

0:18:30.980,0:18:37.660
It was the step Peter took and was coming, and started to drown...

0:18:37.660,0:18:41.520
Finally, when he was about to disappear in the sea...

0:18:41.520,0:18:44.580
Jesus allowed him to test his faith.

0:18:44.580,0:18:48.180
Your faith needs to be tested.

0:18:48.180,0:18:55.000
A relationship must go through hard and good times before it can be mature

0:18:55.000,0:19:00.200
before it can be called a relationship.

0:19:00.200,0:19:15.780
If everything goes smoothly on Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday - I will not wait for Friday

0:19:15.780,0:19:26.320
before going on a fast and pray, "God I am sensing danger."

0:19:26.320,0:19:34.080
This world is not our home; we are only passing through it.

0:19:34.080,0:19:51.540
You are doing a business; big profits from Monday to Thursday - you know you are walking towards danger.

0:19:51.540,0:19:58.840
That profit - something is coming to destroy all the profit you made from Monday to Thursday.

0:19:58.840,0:20:01.880
You have to pause.

0:20:01.880,0:20:11.080
You may not even go to work on Friday because the profit is alarming.

0:20:11.080,0:20:19.200
Monday - profit, Tuesday - profit, Wednesday - profit, Thursday - profit; don't go to work on Friday.

0:20:19.200,0:20:21.220
Avoid what?

0:20:21.220,0:20:23.200
Avoid profit - tell your neighbour.

0:20:23.200,0:20:24.700
[Avoid profit.]

0:20:24.700,0:20:27.340
That profit may be dangerous.

0:20:27.340,0:20:28.340
Just avoid profit.

0:20:28.340,0:20:32.700
Say, "No. Lock the shop. Don't come to my shop and buy - no."

0:20:32.700,0:20:35.340
When someone comes to your shop asking, "Where is that gentleman?"

0:20:35.340,0:20:39.360
they would answer, "He is not around; the shop is not open today."

0:20:39.360,0:20:45.220
Yes, go fast and pray.

0:20:45.220,0:20:52.960
“In this world, there will be tribulation; cheer up, I have overcome for you!”

0:20:52.960,0:20:54.280
[Amen.]

0:20:54.280,0:21:01.760
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:21:01.760,0:21:06.260
Because you don't know you are in the world.

0:21:06.260,0:21:15.140
You don't know how the Bible describes that world to us - believers.

0:21:15.140,0:21:19.900
This world is not my home - sing it for them. 
Let them listen to that song.

