0:22:00.900,0:22:07.360
My treasures are laid up
Somewhere beyond the blue

0:22:07.360,0:22:16.860
The angels beckon me
From Heaven’s open doors

0:22:16.860,0:22:25.600
And I can’t feel at home
In this world any more

0:22:25.600,0:22:28.960
You may be seated.

0:22:28.960,0:22:45.360
Crises, situations, if you are a Christian, are friends and not your enemies.

0:22:45.360,0:22:51.800
When you begin to see your situation as a friend, you will overcome it.

0:22:51.800,0:23:00.660
Because you know you are the cause of your situation, that is why you see it as an enemy but it is not.

0:23:00.660,0:23:04.420
They are meant to promote you.

0:23:04.420,0:23:08.180
The examination you are doing for promotion, are they enemies?

0:23:08.180,0:23:08.920
[No.]

0:23:08.920,0:23:13.060
That is the way, that is the life.

0:23:13.060,0:23:19.460
You have done a lot of examinations to be where you are today.

0:23:19.460,0:23:25.120
Examinations are not enemies; they are enemies when you are not prepared for them.

0:23:25.120,0:23:29.180
When the examination comes and you are not prepared, it becomes an enemy to you

0:23:29.180,0:23:34.540
but when you prepare for an examination, you pray, you are happy – it is your friend.

0:23:34.540,0:23:36.320
Everybody - people pray...

0:23:36.320,0:23:43.840
Those who want to be promoted pray for examination all the time because they want to be promoted.

0:23:43.840,0:23:48.040
When the examination comes and you pass, you’re promoted;

0:23:48.040,0:23:51.220
that is the situation to you, Christians.

0:23:51.220,0:24:00.080
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:24:00.080,0:24:06.840
