0:29:47.540,0:29:52.580
Why are you living as a Christian, as if there will no more be challenges or temptations?

0:29:52.580,0:29:57.460
There will be trouble and situations

0:29:57.460,0:30:03.820
but those situations, challenges and temptations are meant for your spiritual benefit.

0:30:03.820,0:30:07.340
Benefit means to promote you.

0:30:07.340,0:30:14.300
When you face a situation, you are not alone; after that situation, you are up.

