Your spirit must be free and if our spirit is free, joy and happiness comes

0:32:24.100,0:32:28.400
but when you are not free, your spirit is not free and you are worried,

0:32:28.400,0:32:36.800
forget about it– that is not for the Holy Spirit; the Holy Spirit is not allowed at that moment.

0:32:36.800,0:32:42.440
So, satan wants you to be sad all the time because he knows what it means to be sad;

0:32:42.440,0:32:50.000
to be sad is to be out of God; to be unhappy is to be out of God.

0:32:50.000,0:32:54.520
He knows that when you are sad, you are out of God

0:32:54.520,0:32:58.180
and he doesn’t want you to be with God, he wants you to be out of God.

0:32:58.180,0:33:02.280
When you are not happy, you are out of God.

